            "text": "On the Jewish Festivals",
            "html": "<strong>On the Jewish Festivals</strong>"
          },
          {
            "text": "The theme of this letter is the abrogation of the Jewish festivals by the evangelical law. It has no claim to be considered a work of Jerome."
          }
